Welcom to the instructsion panel of our project.

Steps:

Unzip the HRMS.zip file.
Start the xampp Apache server and mysql from the xampp control panel.
Place the HRMS folder unzipped from the .zip file into the public folder htdocs folder in the xampp directory
Configure the database in the ./app/config/database.php
	on the connections array, write the database credentials
Import the attached sql file
Access the project from  http://localhost/HRMS/public/

First, the default login page will come.
Here, the email address acts as the userid. 
Default manager/main admin:
	email: chris@scotch.io
	password: awesome
